data.description: WELCOME HOME! Former Glenn Wright model home w/custom finishes in&out. 5bed 4bth situated on desirable, X large lot in La Preserve: Be transported to a Georgian style community: Treelined streets, winding paths, footbridges & gazebos. Highly coveted, gated community w/only 67 homes minutes from it all! HOME: widened driveway for 3 cars, cul-de-sac, fully fenced, nestled w/mature trees, high ceilings, chiseled edge travertine tile, bedroom & full bath on 1st floor. Gourmet kitchen, lavish finishes: 36" glass cooktop, crown molding, trayed ceilings, 2 newer AC units, pool newly resurfaced, new pavers, heated, salt water, jacuzzi spa & large back yard w/covered entertaining off kitchen. 5th bedrm showing as upstairs loft. Many features to list. Home constructed incomparable to recent builds.
